\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3234388 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2637935\charrsid10688734 Was your mother an easy person to talk to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3104812 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2637935\charrsid10688734 Yes, she was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3234388 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2637935\charrsid10688734 Did she show affection?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3104812 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2637935\charrsid10688734 Yes, she did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3234388 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2637935\charrsid10688734 If there was something worrying you could you go to her and explain these things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3104812 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2637935\charrsid10688734 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3234388 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2637935\charrsid10688734 What about your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3104812 WO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2637935\charrsid10688734 Oh he was just the same as her. But
 the things was there wasn't any need to tell anything to father. 'Cos if something was worrying you, your mother knew. And so if there was anything }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5637547\charrsid10688734 worrying}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
